NYCC 2022 is in the books, and with it, some juicy news and rumors have comic book fans buzzin' about their favorite characters. Join us as we disucss the news, rumors and scuttlebutt that went on this week as well as an in-depth recap and review of the Marvel Cinematic Universe Special Presentation WEREWOLF BY NIGHT! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

